Login (validation); Registration (validation); Logout
Should not be able to navigate to any page outside of Login/Registration without first logging in.
Home page has a listing of all current activities, their creators, and time frames
Past activities should no longer be listed on the Home page
Activities are listed in ascending order according to the date/time of the activity, with the oldest activity at the top
Ability to Join/Leave/Delete an activity from both Home and Activity show pages
Activity show page should list all other users (not created) who have joined.
Users can create new activities, providing all information relating to the activity as well as a start time and duration (validation)
Activities can not be joined if their times/durations conflict with one another